<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Story on ongoing's blog</title><link>https://ongoingblog.org/categories/story/</link><description>Recent content in Story on ongoing's blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 22:55:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ongoingblog.org/categories/story/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>少女终末旅行</title><link>https://ongoingblog.org/2021/11/shoujo-shuumatsu-ryokou/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 22:55:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ongoingblog.org/2021/11/shoujo-shuumatsu-ryokou/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="travel.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不要悲伤
夜幕渐广&lt;/p>
&lt;p>我们看到
那轮霜月隐笑&lt;/p>
&lt;p>将清寒的月光
洒满苍野&lt;/p>
&lt;p>而后
握紧彼此双手共入梦乡&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不要悲伤
终焉也即将登场&lt;/p>
&lt;p>目随万物沉寂
酣然入眠&lt;/p>
&lt;p>而我们那
小小的十字架
就将伫立在
雪白的路旁&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不必再计较
骤雨洗礼
细雪点缀&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不必再追寻
何处吹来的风
飘扬在哪个远方&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>